The app now supports Apple Speech Recognition Technology real time voice recognition significantly enhances the speed of your translations Speech to speech mode is available for Basque and Galician Speech to text translations are now supported for Afrikaans Bulgarian Filipino Icelandic Latin Lithuanian Persian Slovenian Serbian Zulu Text to text translations now also work for Amharic Corsican Frisian Kurdish Kurmanji Luxembourgish Pashto Samoan Shona Sindhi Tatar Xhosa Scottish Gaelic Bashkir Udmurt Querétaro Otomi Yucatec Maya Performance and stability improvements for flawless work on iOS 10. The latest update comes with significant performance improvements: we ve optimized the translation speed and fixed minor bugs to provide flawless user experience. iPad Pro support: the app has been optimized to run smoothly on your new device. Thank you for your continued support and comments submitted by email! Don t hesitate to share your impressions and feedback with us via support apalon.com

This update has new 3D Touch feature for iPhone 6s and iPhone 6s Plus. Hard press on the app icon to quickly send text for translation. Now Speak Translate also takes less space on your device Thank you for your continued support and feedback! We re committed to making the app even better so never lose the drive to share your impressions and feedback with us!

Speak Translate is ready for iOS 9! Try out multitasking enhancements of new iOS on your iPad: make translations simultaneously with browsing reading creating texts or chatting in other apps. All you need is to invoke Slide Over and enter Split View. Translations search is now handier! Improved iOS 9 search allows to access previously made translations through Spotlight search results as well as Siri suggestions. You ll definitely make a good use of our additional improvements: We built offline voices in so that you could reduce Internet traffic use and translate even quicker. In text to text mode you can translate even a text written in language you can t recognize. Choose Detect Language option in language settings and the app will recognize it in a second! Make the app sound as you like just select voice gender male or female.
Performance and stability improvements. Thank you for the comments submitted by email. We appreciate your feedback and are constantly working on making the app better.

Handoff feature: switch from your iPhone to your iPad or vice versa with no problems just tap Handoff icon on your iPad and continue working without interrupting your session all your possible changes and editions will automatically appear on your iPad screen. So keep on working with no delays! iCloud integration: from now on the history of your translations will be synchronized across all your Apple devices! Landscape mode: now available for iPhone 6 and iPad New languages for text to text translation: Armenian Chichewa Kazakh Malagasy Malayalam Myanmar Burmese Sesotho Sinhala Sundanese Tajik Uzbek UX enhancements and bug fix: working with Speak Translate has never been so easy!
